<HEADLINE>
SURVEY: SENIORS FINDING LIFE GOOD UNDER THE COVERS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Will also move in the ``n'' California news file.) 
BY LISA VAN PROYEN  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
