<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-29 01:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9362 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  PM-BUDGET-NYT     09-29 1651
</HEADER>
<BODY>
 PM-BUDGET-NYT 
 (nk) 
