<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-29 16:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0377 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1S     09-29 0633
</HEADER>
