   MIDEAST-U.S. (Washington) _ President Clinton met Tuesday with
Yasser Arafat, the Palestinian leader, in what aides described as a
determined attempt to complete an interim agreement between Israel
and Palestinians within a few weeks. By Steven Erlanger.
