</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   DELTA-AD-COLUMN (Undated) _ Humor is not a common element in
airline advertising. Maybe that is because so many travelers these
days find nothing funny about flying. Nonetheless, Delta Air Lines
is using humor as the central element in the first television
campaign for its low-fare airline, Delta Express. By Courtney Kane.
</P>
