   1998 .254 124 23 75 4
</P>
<P>
   LEFT FIELD: Henry Rodriguez
</P>
<P>
   Sometimes Henry Rodriguez is a star, sometimes not. Rodriguez,
who had a strong first half, is hitting .211 this month. He can be
very dangerous with runners on base, although he might not start
Game 1 because he is 2-for-22 against Smoltz. Then again, he also
struggles against Maddux (8-for-35) and Glavine (2-for-17).
</P>
