</P>
<P>
   CATCHER: Tyler Houston
</P>
<P>
   The Cubs platoon Tyler Houston and Scott Servais at catcher. But
the left-handed-hitting Houston, a former Brave, continues to
improve and caught Monday's playoff game. Houston was 6-for-20 as a
pinch hitter. Servais will get the start against Braves lefty Tom
Glavine and is 0-for-12 as a pinch hitter this season.
</P>
<P>
   Houston Avg. H HR RBI SB
</P>
<P>
   vs. Braves .167 1 0 1 0
</P>
