<P>
   BENCH
</P>
<P>
   The Cubs have a nice supply of talent, including Orlando Merced,
Glenallen Hill, Brant Brown, Matt Mieske and Manny Alexander. Brown
is used against some right-handers and is the club's main
left-handed pinch hitter. He is 6-for-20 with four RBIs in that
role. Hill is having a super season after coming over from the
Mariners. He is 4-for-13 with two homers and seven RBIs in
pinch-hitting duties. Alexander is used some as a defensive
replacement at short.
</P>
