<P>
   PITCHING STAFF
</P>
<P>
   NO. 1 STARTER: Mark Clark
</P>
<P>
   Because the Cubs were unable to set up their rotation for the
postseason and had to win a one-game playoff, they will have to go
with Mark Clark in the opener. Clark has been inconsistent all
season, and his ERA has risen steadily over the last three years.
</P>
