</P>
<P>
   NO. 2 STARTER: Kevin Tapani
</P>
<P>
   Kevin Tapani, who returned last year from injury, led the team
in wins with 19. Tapani, who started and lost to Houston on Friday,
had to work more than an inning in relief in Monday's playoff game
and was charged with two runs. His ERA was a relatively high 4.85.
</P>
