<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: PRICELINE.COM EXPANDS TO HOTELS; NEW SWISS
AIRLINE; SHUTTLE'S NEW BOSTON HOME; TRAIN TO COPENHAGEN AIRPORT;
HOTEL UPDATE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Conn., N.J., Mass., Ill., Colo.)  (Also moved in ``f'' category.) 
